  <refnamediv>
    <refname>Modelica_initialize</refname>
    <refpurpose>Menu: Opens the Modelica implicit model initialization GUI.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
      The initialization (finding a compatible initial state) of a implicit system  is often a difficult problem. 
      The Modelica model initialization interacative tool has been built to help user in this task.
    </para>
    <para>
      Executing this menu compiles the Modelica diagram (if necessary), and
      launches the Modelica initialization GUI.
    </para>
  </refsection>
